data.description:
Roof 2018
Welcome to the Tortoise View Townhomes. A beachside community tucked away in Satellite beach just off of South Patrick Dr near Pineda.  This single level townhome has 2 bedrooms and easily a 3rd currently used as a large office (just add a door) and 2 full baths. Spacious living area, dining room and eat-in kitchen with inside laundry closet.  Screened back porch nearly runs the length of the rear and roll down hurricane shutters make storm prep a breeze.   The interior is ready for some fresh updates and therefore reflected in the pricing.   A fun project in a fantastic location.   Two car garage. Low HOA includes lawn care and pool maintenance.
